column5: Hi, Is there a bait shop heading west from Fort Frances? I am aware of the shop heading east next to the Bayview Motel. And if there is one do they sell oxygen bag minnows? Thanks, Nimstug When I Grow Up, I Want to be a Little Boy
We used to stop at a place named "Witherspoons" there---maybe that will help you.
Nimstug A buddy was in Fort Frances 2-3 weeks ago. He said the bait shop on the west side of town was closed then.
